snippet: This week could clear up the Bowl Championship Series or bolster the likelihood that at least three teams will finish the regular season undefeated.
abstract: Analysis; three Week 11 college football games laden with Bowl Championship Series implications will help clear a logjam of undefeated teams atop the rankings or bolster the likelihood that at least three will finish the season without a loss.
lead_paragraph: This week could clear up the Bowl Championship Series or bolster the likelihood that at least three teams will finish the regular season undefeated.

headline.main: A B.C.S. Logjam, Possibly, to End Them All
